---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { url } from '../utils/url';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy" description="ReefMetric privacy policy.">
  <section class="container" style="max-width:760px;">
    <p class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--brand-2)">Legal</p>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: July 2026.</em></p>
    <p>ReefMetric respects your privacy. This page explains what we collect and why.</p>
    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <p>Today, ReefMetric runs no analytics and sets no first-party cookies. If you subscribe to our email list, we collect the address you provide and never sell it. This page will be updated — before it happens, not after — if we add analytics or tracking.</p>
    <h2>Cookies &amp; consent</h2>
    <p>We don't currently set analytics or tracking cookies. When you click a "Check price" link, you leave ReefMetric for the retailer's site, and that retailer may set its own cookies under its own privacy policy — that's between you and them, not us. If we add on-site analytics in the future, EU/UK visitors will be shown a consent banner and US visitors will be able to opt out via Global Privacy Control (GPC) before any tracking cookie is set.</p>
    <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
    <p>Some links are affiliate links — see our <a href={url('/disclosure')}>Affiliate Disclosure</a>.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Reach us at <a href="mailto:hello@reefmetric.com">hello@reefmetric.com</a>.</p>
  </section>
</Base>
